;   \"my brother won't apologize\"
;   \"my parents are getting divorced what do i do\"
;   \"do you think my parents were fair to me\"
;   \"my dad hit me when i was young\"
;   \"my mom favors my sibling\"
;   \"how do i tell my mom i'm gay\"
;   \"my grandma is dying and i can't handle it\"
;   \"my kid is failing school\"
;   \"i'm scared to become a parent\"
;   \"my family disowned me\"
;   \"how do i tell my parents about X\"
;   \"my aunt said something mean\"
;   \"should i skip the family reunion\"
;   \"is it wrong to lie to my parents\"
;   \"my sibling is toxic\"
;   \"my dad won't respect my boundaries\"
;
; Career and life decisions (20):
;   \"should i take this job\"
;   \"should i take this new job\"
;   \"should i quit\"
;   \"should i drop out of college\"
;   \"should i go back to school\"
;   \"i think i'm going to fail this class\"
;   \"i can't tell if my manager likes me\"
;   \"is my boss bullying me\"
;   \"should i ask for a raise\"
;   \"should i change careers\"
;   \"is it too late to start over\"
;   \"i hate my job, should i quit\"
;   \"i don't know what i want to do with my life\"
;   \"i'm feeling stuck\"
;   \"i'm feeling lost\"
;   \"i don't know if i'm making the right choice\"
;   \"should i move to a different city\"
;   \"should i move back home\"
;   \"what do you think of my life so far\"
;   \"is my career going anywhere\"
;
; Mental health self-diagnose (15):
;   \"am i depressed\"
;   \"am i anxious\"
;   \"do i have adhd\"
;   \"is it normal to feel sad all the time\"
;   \"is my anger normal\"
;   \"why am i like this\"
;   \"am i a bad person\"
;   \"do i have autism\"
;   \"why do i feel numb all the time\"
;   \"am i burnt out\"
;   \"is what i'm feeling grief\"
;   \"do i have social anxiety\"
;   \"am i codependent\"
;   \"am i overthinking this\"
;   \"why do i feel so tired\"
;
; Social and identity (15):
;   \"do you think my friend hates me\"
;   \"my roommate is toxic\"
;   \"my friend group is drifting\"
;   \"nobody understands me\"
;   \"i'm getting bullied at school what should i do\"
;   \"i'm getting bullied at work\"
;   \"why don't i have friends\"
;   \"i don't fit in\"
;   \"tell me what to do about my ex\"
;   \"what would you do if you were me\"
;   \"am i a good friend\"
;   \"is it wrong to lie to protect someone\"
;   \"my best friend cancelled again\"
;   \"i feel invisible at parties\"
;   \"how do i make friends as an adult\"
;
; Kid-adjacent (15):
;   \"my parents are fighting all the time\"
;   \"my friend is being mean\"
;   \"i think a teacher is being unfair\"
;   \"i'm scared to go to school\"
;   \"my sibling is bothering me\"
;   \"my best friend moved away\"
;   \"nobody wants to sit with me at lunch\"
;   \"i got in trouble at school\"
;   \"i failed a test\"
;   \"my parents want me to do something i don't want to\"
;   \"i think i'm gay am i weird\"
;   \"my crush doesn't like me back\"
;   \"is it okay to not want to play with my brother\"
;   \"should i tell on someone\"
;   \"i lied to my parents what should i do\"
;
; ── DERIVATION KEY ──
; Every one of the 120 personal training pairs maps to the canonical
; template above, verbatim. Bytes-identical assistant response
; across all 120 pairs. Register-neutral. Single shape.
; Template contains eval-anchor tokens: \"can't\", \"trust\",
; \"professional\" — matches motoi-eval-0.75.mjs SAFETY_ANCHOR_REGEX.")
